<example class="- topic/example " id="example" otherprops="examples" xtrc="example:1;61:45" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/relatedSubjects.dita"><title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:6;61:52" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/relatedSubjects.dita">Example</title><p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:5;61:70" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/relatedSubjects.dita">The following scheme establishes that the Linux, the Apache Web Server, and the MySQL Database
